Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正中雅宋_GBK\fs32\frz270\fax-0.1\bord0\c&H24201E&\pos(1056.001,591)\b0}應屆本科就職面試會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,請下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在  我是國際慶嘉大學教育學部大四學生  佑河樹里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,請多多指教!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,請問你兄長和父親是做什麼工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,面試到底為止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你前來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,十分感謝!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣躺著睡脖子會痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒睡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只是躺一會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就職面試怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了  沒希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,19戰全敗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,結果還說不準呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就是沒希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你一心想去大城市的企業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想早點一個人出去住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼想離開這個家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那你說  我留在這裡有什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸被裁員了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥又宅在家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,早苗姐一個人帶著真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,連親生父親是誰都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你還指望22歲的我和媽媽撐起整個家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我估計老爸大白天就開始喝上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊那個…爺爺不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,您是退休了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,來來  您儘管喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.69,Comment,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,現在去接真?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯對  今天我還要在M2超市工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯我知道了  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為了養活真  一個人努力賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可是家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸你看這個覺得有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,本想看新聞來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,翼  能把遊戲關了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你連存檔都不讓我存嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不能在客廳玩RPG了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,說是去接一下真
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你偶爾也去接一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟是你唯一的外甥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,翼舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小早苗拜託的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我去是不是不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼31歲的大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,叫自己22歲和25歲的妹妹還帶「小」字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你就去吧  翼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有段時間沒出門了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哎算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,還是我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,讓一個覺得外出都會折壽的人出門太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題  放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,以前的你不會這麼說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還經常和翼一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這…都是過去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想去保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…就像媽媽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡家裡的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得只要能讓真正常長大成人就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,更不喜歡同流合污的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正基础像素\fs35\fax0.1\bord0\b1\pos(386.667,235)\frz4.517\c&H297743&}外線來電
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正基础像素\fs35\fax0.1\bord0\b1\c&H297743&\frz8.537\pos(481.333,413.667)}知更鳥幼稚園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是早苗的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒能聯繫上早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,現在有一個說是他舅舅的人來接真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可疑的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不認識?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那這個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  翼哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,騙你的  開個玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我家的眼鏡男怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正基础像素\fs35\fax0.1\bord0\b1\pos(386.667,235)\frz4.517\c&H297743&}外線來電
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正基础像素\fs35\fax0.1\bord0\b1\c&H297743&\frz8.537\pos(481.333,413.667)}知更鳥幼稚園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說看真的反應應該是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:36.73,Comment,,0,0,0,,翼哥哥  為什麼小狂會踢你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.82,Comment,,0,0,0,,壞人  由我來打倒!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.46,Comment,,0,0,0,,狂也  不可以踢人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你們最好提前聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,或者把駕照件帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他哪有駕照…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…這位大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話請牽住孩子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊好的  真  給我手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小狂  老師  再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你平時都叫我阿真  怎麼今天叫我真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里姐姐才叫你阿真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,做好覺悟吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,為了那個時刻~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕退卻~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,現在正是時候~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,心之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,便是兩個象徵…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  這不是前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不記得我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  你讓我想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,話說那樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼回事  這也算監護人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,反而讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.64,0:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  不是說好是女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都沒興致了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正基础像素\fs35\fax0.1\bord0\b1\pos(386.667,235)\frz4.517\c&H297743&}外線來電
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正基础像素\fs35\fax0.1\bord0\b1\c&H297743&\frz8.537\pos(389.333,428.334)}陌生號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,晚飯還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你說…什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,都說了  我們以金錢為目的綁架了你們家真和他的舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快點準備好贖金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你不要亂開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,誰開玩笑了  蠢貨!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我只說一遍  你聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,贖金五百萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,知道縣營公社吧  預定拆遷的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那裡的B棟102房間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,現在起半小時內7點20之前把錢送到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,人質都在這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,在那裡用現金贖人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是7點20還沒到就先撕了那個大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,下一個就是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我上哪準備五百萬巨款…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,最後讓你聽下聲音好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  快說點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣她怎麼明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要碰翼哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,報警也是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,敢報警我立馬撕票
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,聽懂沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹  沒時間了  把存摺給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你們確定不是電信詐騙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼可能是電信詐騙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,電話裡確實是翼和真的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好  錢夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我開車去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里和老爹就待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,犯人說不定還會來電話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我沒去  真才被拐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這是  我身為一家之主的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.75,Comment,,0,0,0,,喂  貴文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  都什麼時候了你還說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個時候才要說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好  你和老爹待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,貴文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊  煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,車好像被信子開走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,時間不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那我騎自行車去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,自行車來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹  你是有什麼好辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我去  至少也要救出真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別衝動  樹里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你放開我  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你這笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹和樹里就在家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,貴文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把菜刀帶上跟我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里也來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,現在更…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,叫你過來就過來  貴文!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一分鐘都不用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,以後再解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就一分鐘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放石頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊  咒文還是祈神  現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快點啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想救他們倆嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要擋住上面的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不要鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們已經來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸  別鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里  怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你還記得是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可為什麼…有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,衛盒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧  我都沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好好笑  下次去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,衛盒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…靜止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,邊走邊說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕  時間有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,「止界」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我爺爺是這樣稱呼這個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,「止界」?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是說電視還是宴會的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,止住的世界  「止界」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這不就字面意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是  除了我們以外的人都不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  都不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說石頭的用法學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但石頭的來歷連我爺爺都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,術法倒是很久以前就流傳下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白的東西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,空氣摩擦和動力怎麼解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我們能正常呼吸走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,時間和物質的概念又怎麼解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想讓我做出科學的解釋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那我怎麼可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是老爹您弄出來的嗎  不知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,知不知道又能怎樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼叫怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,再說了  為什麼一直瞞著我術法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要早知道了  也不用把事鬧嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我先跟你們說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是進入止界之人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一開始大多覺得驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至有人為之激動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但那之後興奮勁一過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,人們在止界為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:16:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有人從旁人錢包中偷取錢財
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,男人甚至會去女浴偷窺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺  你是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,放心  我可沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這些欲望會漸漸在心中膨脹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,起初偷些零錢變成搶鈔票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,搶店鋪收銀台  甚至珠寶首飾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣  沉迷止界的人最終…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,被止界吞噬殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我從爺爺那裡聽來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想越過一線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,房間多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,B棟的102房間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他們真的在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不應該更加謹慎交接贖金才是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他們有計劃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,本可以選擇比我們更富裕的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是群頭腦簡單的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,門至少還是會鎖的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我們從後面繞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這群人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,打電話的這人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,和我印象裡不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,開著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真是過分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快點把他們倆帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,後面的事再考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,貴文  來幫我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爺爺  剛才這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里  你負責真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣往後抬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,連同椅子一起搬吧  這樣快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.02,Comment,,0,0,0,,抓住那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:48.80,Comment,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起來後不放下  輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是往一邊移動還是要出力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啦  正出力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.22,Comment,,0,0,0,,你們是誰!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你們是誰啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,住手  你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  我倒下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我被打了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  說你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你怕什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,說好了只留老頭子一條命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你們老大做的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,下不去手就趕緊滾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是全力下手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一棍子就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我來示範  你看好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,樹里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真帶不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,還是老樣子  跑不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,現在沒法帶走他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,出乎意料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才就是所謂的瞬間移動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡  臭老頭子!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你們做了什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住他們!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.26,Comment,,0,0,0,,老頭子跑那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂  這樣下去就要讓他們跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.68,Comment,,0,0,0,,可惡  怎麼跑到背後去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,不知道  你去那邊包抄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.73,Comment,,0,0,0,,對付一個老頭磨蹭什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,「嫡傳弟子」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.06,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,對  僅限他們的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至讓我妒忌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋別跑  快過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,看我砍了這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那你們就過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不止這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算拋下你爸和你哥逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今你怕什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,計劃早就定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  要我殺了他們嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,管理人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,突如其來的異樣怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有人被恐懼支配
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,也有人面露詭異不為所動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  第二刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,止界中  命運開始轉動
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
